# Prompt Examples

## Initial Concept

I want to create an application that visualizes a human life using a grid of weeks. Each square represents one week. Users should be able to mark life events such as birthdays, travel, or important milestones.

## UI Design Prompt

Please redesign the color palette to make it light, airy, and modern with white and sky-blue gradients.

## Feature Expansion Prompt

Add the ability to select multiple weeks and apply an event to the entire interval.

## Bug Fix Prompt

Birthdays are shifting by one day each year. Please fix the calculation so that the same date appears every year.
